MP DOCUMENTATION:
Manual

  Our game is called “Pokerots: UP Tacloban Edition” which entails the implementation of a game modeled after classic Pokémon emulator games, but with a unique alteration. Instead of utilizing established Pokémon characters, the game will feature "Italian Brainrot" characters. These AI-generated fictional characters gained significant popularity through social media platforms such as TikTok, Instagram Reels, and YouTube Shorts.

Furthermore, the game will adopt the UP Tacloban Campus as the central "map" or environment. Key mechanics from the traditional Pokémon games will be incorporated, including "Gym Leaders" serving as our “mini” boss challenges, and the core functionality of catching, owning, and engaging in battles with other Pokerots. 

Overall the purpose of our game is to incorporate the well established fighting system and the fun gameplay of the classic Pokemon arcade game, with something that resonates and appeals more to the trends and interests of us the developers and to the people of the younger generation.






